{"tid":1221944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 物資 ] 自己物資自己帶！！！人人都係物資站！！","createTime":"2019-06-14T10:24:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T07:01:11.000Z","uid":35699,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2cf272e0dc106a1a30d9a41182cc7c4a629fbd44","tid":1221944,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:24:54.000Z","msg":"大家發夢都記得物資站總係攻擊目標，狗隻對大量物資嘅地方好敏感，所以應該提倡「人人物資站」呢個概念，適當攜帶野餐物資，享受野餐嘅樂趣！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nA）自己需要嘅物資<br />\n1. 頭盔<br />\n2. 手套<br />\n3. 眼罩口罩 / 防毒面具<br />\n<br />\n呢三種一定要帶喇！話晒喺大自然野餐有好多猛獸侵擾，要好好保護自己先可以開餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nB) 助人物資<br />\n1. 生理鹽水（細排都可以）<br />\n2. 少量食物<br />\n3. 水 五百毫升或以上<br />\n4. 膠布 或其他可用物資<br />\n<br />\n呢幾類物資可能你都唔識用，不過帶住喺身好過到時要傳嚟傳去，除咗自己帶備之外，都可以喺野餐場地嘅物資站物資充裕嘅情況下攞少少以上物資龐身，咁就可以隨時幫到自己又幫到人啦！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有狗或者野獸爭物資，你嘅機動性都可以令物資免受破壞，唔好為呢個地球製造更多塑膠垃圾嘛！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78039ec8eb03326dc80d92abd49ee293361b3943","tid":1221944,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:39:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8556293d652845910d7f1219347f5b967182ebdb","tid":1221944,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:13:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54bfe483cec2d1c9bee77869a47af288e6cbf287","tid":1221944,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"020612f7ded09cf07ffe97ec7ac0d97fc8c56bd2","tid":1221944,"uid":35699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:25:40.000Z","msg":"你地繼續依賴物資站啦，啲狗掃晒啲嘢你哋等食屎"},{"pid":"3949d8f088de8a888de7a652e362b18f7f8b8d56","tid":1221944,"uid":200799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T04:45:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca293999b45f75086a18e8fb4b2bf863a3e06146","tid":1221944,"uid":200799,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T04:45:37.000Z","msg":"物資唔可以太集中"},{"pid":"831b136b8db59f963689f74adb01d1d47f884c86","tid":1221944,"uid":200799,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T04:45:55.000Z","msg":"一撒退就收皮"},{"pid":"c7122518ac9b1c28a184c647b7d884e636d67749","tid":1221944,"uid":200799,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T04:46:16.000Z","msg":"物資一定要流動"},{"pid":"9476a0e2351b66aa7b0eeefc532488edfb63f328","tid":1221944,"uid":200799,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T04:47:14.000Z","msg":"最好一人一個背包 <br />\n入面袋D必需品"},{"pid":"99e713c61f10578fdb2d2d8561b176728d509541","tid":1221944,"uid":200799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T04:48:51.000Z","msg":"一人袋一支鹽水 咁就可以去到邊救到邊<br />\n唔使下下人傳人問"},{"pid":"2a2256a9027d2df625a427174f5dae33442620be","tid":1221944,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:01:11.000Z","msg":"push"}]}